last_episode_to_air.name: Summer Friends / Last Day of Camp
last_episode_to_air.overview: With camp nearing its end, Sally faces saying goodbye to her new friend Naomi. Snoopy and the Beagle Scouts race to earn one last badge.

name: Camp Snoopy
overview: After discovering their troop is in danger of disbanding, Snoopy and the Beagle Scouts set off to the great outdoors to earn their badges. Meanwhile, Charlie Brown and friends enjoy their summer at Camp Spring Lake.

episodes.name: A Beagle Scout Prepares / Teach a Bird to Fish
episodes.overview: Snoopy takes action after hearing his troop is at risk of being dissolved. The Beagle Scouts set out to earn their fishing badges.

episodes.name: Homesick Sally / Red Haired Letter Day
episodes.overview: Sally struggles to adjust to camp—but a new friend hops into her life. Charlie Brown enlists Snoopy's help to deliver a special letter.

episodes.name: To Dive or Not to Dive / Foul Weather Friends
episodes.overview: Peppermint Patty's fear of diving sends her Snoopy's way. The Beagle Scouts attempt to build a shelter as Sally and Naomi fight over bracelets.

episodes.name: Blueberry Birds / A Banner Day
episodes.overview: Snoopy and the Beagle Scouts embark on a mission to earn their foraging badges. Charlie Brown is determined to win a "Piney" award.

episodes.name: Campfire Yarns / Beagle Point or Bust
episodes.overview: The kids tell scary campfire stories, but Charlie Brown is lost for words. Snoopy's journal sheds light on an ill-fated canoe voyage to Beagle Point.

episodes.name: Beagle vs Bug / Camp Song
episodes.overview: Snoopy encounters a new nemesis: a mosquito that won't leave him alone. Schroeder thinks the camp's official song is due for an update.

episodes.name: Leave It Like You Found It / Camp Mascot
episodes.overview: The Beagle Scouts and the kids enjoy a hidden oasis, but their playtime upsets Linus. Charlie Brown and Snoopy compete to be camp mascot.

episodes.name: Farewell, My Blanket / Operation Pizza
episodes.overview: Linus' blanket gets snagged and unravels on a hike, leaving him frazzled. Snoopy tries to crash the kids' build-your-own-pizza night.

episodes.name: Bed Heads & Beagle Care / The Great Gold Rush
episodes.overview: Snoopy wants the Beagle Scouts to try for the dog-care badge—by pampering him. A scavenger hunt sends the kids on a wild goose chase.

episodes.name: Ring Toss / Letters Home
episodes.overview: Sally feels left out when Naomi and Snoopy play ring toss. The kids write home about their best days at camp.

episodes.name: Camp Crush / Counselor for a Day
episodes.overview: Peppermint Patty is convinced Charlie Brown has a crush on her and wants to let him down easy. Marcie is chosen to be camp counselor for a day.

episodes.name: Sally's Tooth / The Chewing Gum Dilemma
episodes.overview: Sally loses a tooth and worries the tooth fairy won't know she's at camp. Charlie Brown's fortunate find turns into candy chaos.

episodes.name: Summer Friends / Last Day of Camp
episodes.overview: With camp nearing its end, Sally faces saying goodbye to her new friend Naomi. Snoopy and the Beagle Scouts race to earn one last badge.
